      <details>
        <summary>How do message credits work in Chatbase?</summary>
        <p>Credits are consumed each time your AI agent generates a response. The rate varies by model: 1 credit for GPT-4o Mini and Claude 3.5 Sonnet, up to 5 credits for Claude Opus 4.6. Credits reset on the 1st of every month. When credits run out, the agent shows an unavailability message until credits renew or you purchase more via auto-recharge at $40 per 1,000 credits.</p>
