        <summary>Is Chatbase safe and secure?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Chatbase holds SOC 2 Type II certification, is GDPR compliant, uses AES-256 encryption for all data at rest and in transit, and added SSO in January 2026. Crucially, your data is never used to train AI models — the RAG architecture retrieves your data at query time without exposing it to model training. Additional protections include domain allowlisting, rate limiting, and role-based access controls.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What are Chatbase AI Actions?</summary>
        <p>AI Actions let your agent perform real tasks during conversations — not just answer questions. The AI can autonomously check order status via API calls, book meetings through Calendly or Cal.com, process billing queries via Stripe, create support tickets in Zendesk, capture lead information, trigger custom webhooks, and connect to 5,000+ apps via Zapier and Make. Available AI Actions per agent: 5 (Hobby), 8 (Standard), 12 (Pro).</p>
