      <details>
        <summary>How is Chatbase different from FastBots.ai?</summary>
        <p>Chatbase is the more advanced option: it offers 15+ AI models vs FastBots.ai's more limited selection, includes AI Actions for task automation, has SOC 2 certification, supports 6 native deployment channels, and includes voice support. FastBots.ai has a free tier and is simpler to set up for basic FAQ chatbots. Chatbase is better for businesses that need intelligent, action-taking AI agents with compliance requirements. FastBots.ai is better for simple FAQ automation on a tight budget.</p>
